Implementado:
- `AttachmentServiceApplication.java` — ponto de entrada
- `config/RabbitMQConfig.java` — apenas a TopicExchange declarada
- `dto/PresignedUrlResponse.java` (record) — url, fileKey, fileName, contentType
- `dto/AttachmentConfirmRequest.java` (record) — fileKey, fileName, contentType, sizeBytes, entityId, entityType, gpsLat, gpsLng
